e5 Nh5 9. Bg3 c5 10. Nb3 d4 11. Ne4 Qd5 12. Qe2 Nxg3 13. Nxg3 Nc6 $15 {0-1 (24)
Martin,A (2440)-Okhotnik,V (2400) Douai 1993}) 8... Bb4 ({An error is} 8... c6
