}) 13. f3 Nf8 14. Rb1 b5 15. Nc7 $16 {The knight on c7 is not going to be
captured and White's advantage is clear.}) 9. O-O-O c6 {This is undoubtedly
the best way to continue for the second player, giving rise to very unbalanced
positions.} (9... Nxe4 $2 10. Qxd5 Qxd5 11. Nxd5 Na6 (11... Nc6 $2 12. Be3 $18)
12. Nxb4 Nxb4 13. Nxc7 Nxf2 14. Rd2 Nxh1 15. Nxa8 Re8 16. Be2 $16 {Black is
